entries.next: Mesa no have nutten for yousa to be doin. Mesa busy. Come backo later and mebbe mesa have sumthin.
entries.cantwork: Yousa seem mooie mooie busy. Come backo when yousa have nutten on yousa brain.
entries.npc_reset_1: Mesa no like whensa yousa not finish mesa maxibig tasks. Come backo whensa yousa can finish da task.
entries.notyet: Mesa no have nutten for yousa right now.
entries.npc_1_1: Heyo. Yousa be needin a task? My be needin someone to hep mesa. Yousa no needin to be smarty. Just needin to tek a gizmo to Naboo maxibig patron. Mesa be payen for de hep. Yousa hep mesa?
entries.npc_2_1: Good. Mesa no like whensa dosen others tink dey so smarty den usan. Dey stinkowiff! But yousa seem okeyday.
entries.npc_3_1: Yousa one of dem! Yousa tink yous brain so big. Mesa no like yousa.
entries.npc_4_1: Yousa needin to go to see Sentellus Gavrel. He be maxibig patron wit mooie mooie moolah. Mesa bosses tink wesa be needin to kiss hisan feet. Make mesa sick!
entries.npc_backtowork_1: Whatsa more yousa be needin? Yousa reconsider?
entries.npc_reward_1: Yousa done a berry good job. Here, tek dis medicine. It hep yousa feel bettah.
entries.npc_work_1: Have yousa tekken da talkie to Naboo smarty patron? Whatsa yousa be waitin for?
entries.npc_noloc_1: Mesa give yousa da location of da Naboo smarty patron soon. Mesa haven to find hesan first.
entries.npc_failure_1: Mesa no like yousa! Off wit yousa! Yousa no better dan dosen smarty others. Yousa all stinkowiff!
entries.otherescort_1: Terribly busy, I'm afraid. Can't talk now.
entries.dontknowyou_1: Terribly busy, I'm afraid. Can't talk now.
entries.npc_breech_1: Can I help you? You seem to be looking for someone!
entries.npc_smuggle_1: Ah, this must be the survey equipment I requested. Excellent! But where is Mullud? Did that lazy good-for-nothing get someone else to do his work again?
entries.gotowork_1: I was expecting some survey equipment. Was that what you meant to give me?
entries.notit_1: No, I need some survey equipment. This is definitely not what I ordered. Likely that good-for-nothing Mullud messed everything up. You probably couldn't understand a word he was trying to say.
entries.player_reset_1: I don't want this mission right now.
entries.player_sorry_1: I'll keep working on the mission.
entries.player_3_1: I think you want me to deliver some equipment. To who exactly?
